Dad, please don't be angry with me.

107
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:20,640
I've been extremely busy with work these past 3 months,

108
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:22,570
so I haven't been able to visit you.

109
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,800
But every week,

110
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,640
