119
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,900
Dad, what's wrong?

120
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:53,640
Aliens are coming to take me home.

121
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,320
Dad, don't joke with me.

122
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,440
